# Product analytics (PostHog)

Product analytics lives in `packages/app/src/analytics/`. Platform init stays in `apps/web` (`instrumentation-client.ts`) and `apps/mobile` (`PostHogRuntime` in `_layout.tsx`).

## APIs (shared code)

| API | When to use |
|-----|-------------|
| `trackProductEvent(event, category, properties?)` | **Default** — outcome events from hooks, handlers, mutations |
| `AnalyticsEvent` | Named constants — never hard-code event strings |
| `useAnalytics()` | Rare — only when you need `identify` / `reset` / low-level capture |

Import from `@app-template/app` or relative `../analytics/...`.

## Do / don't

- **Do** track user-visible outcomes at success-path choke points
- **Don't** import `posthog-js` or `posthog-react-native` in screens — use `trackProductEvent`
- **Don't** track PII beyond what `PostHogAuthSync` already identifies

See root `AGENTS.md` for env vars.
